  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">This blue and gold mithral alloy hand-and-a-half sword can be wielded 2h with martial weapon proficiency, dealing 1.5x strength damage. Or it can be wielded 1h as an exotic weapon proficiency (katana or bastard sword proficiency will suffice). It strikes as magic/gold/silver for DR purposes.</span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">Engraving:</span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">It's blade is engraved with war-prayers that shift and change constantly, but always draw from deities and heroes of good or lawful alignment. As such it functions as a @UUID[Compendium.pf-content.pf-items.Item.qc5oNm0eGSixctIr]{Book of war prayers}, but requiring only 1 minute to recite instead of the usual 10 minutes to receive the @UUID[Compendium.folken-games-carrion-crown-pathfinder-rpg.folken-games-carrion-crown-items-pf1e.Item.T2inWv8ru1hKtCA9]{SuperBless} buff.</span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">Enhancements:</span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">When the blade is held straight up before the wielder's face, it provides the following benefits:</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">The cast time of @UUID[Compendium.pf1.spells.Item.wa0zb2pncesmm9lz]{Bless}, @UUID[Compendium.pf1.spells.Item.hu8179fdqfkl0bqj]{Prayer}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf1.spells.Item.1i8b1v3dngkxj6jp]{Magic Circle against Evil} are reduced to a swift action and their effective radii is doubled.</span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">Offensive:</span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">@UUID[Compendium.pf1.class-abilities.Item.MpvhQz62qw68D2pd]{Bane} effects are empowered by this blade (+3 to hit, 3d6 damage instead of +2/2d6). @UUID[Compendium.pf1.class-abilities.Item.2TsDfK0SKC8IGVx4]{Smite Evil} attacks that cause damage via confirmed critical hit trigger a free @UUID[Compendium.pf1.class-abilities.Item.WhE4j0Jc82npdMCP]{Lay on Hands} on the wielder. @UUID[Compendium.pf1.class-abilities.Item.tHObxrPeyhimmz9V]{Channel Positive Energy} grants those that it heals +1ac per dice the wielder's channel heals, lasting until the wielders next turn.</span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">Defensive:</span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">The wielder is treated as having the @UUID[Compendium.pf-content.pf-feats.Item.DX6vy7YmF0UQVqOG]{Crane Style} feat, reducing their \"fight defensively\" penalty from -4 to -2, and providing an additionaly +1 dodge bonus to ac when using the Fight Defensively or Total Defense action.</span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">Bracing:</span></h3><p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X\">If the wielder braces against a charge, their readied swing vs the target that charges them inflicts double weapon dice and double strength damage.</span></p><img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/sinlaire/mukhlis-nur-sinlaire-sword21-024-origin-cut-copy.webp\" /><p></p>",
